Text: One of the wold oldest religion of the world. Its focus on the human mind in
  deep. Before the modern psychology come as a subject to us Buddhism talks about
  it 2600 years ago. Although Buddhism considers as a religion, when we study it we
  can realize that it is not, it is far beyond religion and it is a philosophy.  It
  is step by steps analysed the human's mind and show the way how to live be happy.
